<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to KhumaloCraft Emporium</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #cfe4ff; /* Creamy off-white background color */
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f9f5f2; /* Light warm brown background color for container */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Rounded corners for container */
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Shadow effect for container */
        }

        h1 {
            color: #5c4637; /* Dark brown text color for heading */
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            color: #5c4637; /* Dark brown text color for paragraphs */
            font-size: 24px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .hero-image {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to KhumaloCraft Emporium</h1>
        <img src="~/Images/bracelets.jpg" alt="Handcrafted marvels" class="hero-image">
        <p>This page serves as the gateway to our website.</p>
        <p>Here, you'll embark on a journey into the realm of handcrafted marvels crafted by artisans worldwide. Explore an array of meticulously crafted treasures waiting to be discovered.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
